item.description: The Juke joint Rhythm Rockers will be rocking Mr. Dooley's in Wrentham.. This is a great venue. No Cover. Nice dance Floor, Great beer, great food great music and the staff make you feel like this is your favorite spot.. Hey this ain't Boston but you don't have to worry about paying for parking... You will love this.. Whoever says they are going and show's up we will give you one of our new CD's that was just released.. This is our pre going on tour show...See you there!!!!
item.name: Juke Joint Rhyhtm Rockers Rocking Mr. Dooleys Wrentham
